          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The results  of  measuring  isomeric  ratios  in (n,g)",
                " reactions with thermal neutrons  and (g,n)  reactions",
                " with  the electron bremsstrahlung of end-point energy",
                " 25 MeV yielding odd-odd  nuclides  190,192,194Ir  and",
                " 196,198Au  are  reported.  The  activation method was",
                " used  to  measure reaction  cross  sections. Isomeric",
                " ratios are calculated within statistical model."
              ]
            }
